# Premium Model Endowment 30/15

## Project Overview
This project demonstrates the calculation process for insurance premium pricing using Google Sheets.

The spreadsheet includes actuarial calculations such as:
- Present Value of Death Benefits
- Present Value of Survival Benefits
- Present Value of Premium Payments
- Lapse-adjusted Present Values
- Net Single Premium
- Net Annual Premium
- Expense Loading
- Gross Premium

## Skills Demonstrated
- Spreadsheet Modeling
- Actuarial Mathematics
- Financial Modeling
- Present Value Calculations

## Key Features
- Dynamic calculations using spreadsheet formulas
- Separate assumption inputs and calculation sections
- Premium calculation based on actuarial principles

